  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age &gt;18 years old

          -  ulcerative colitis patients without symptoms for at least 1 year

          -  ulcerative colitis patients who undergo colonoscopy for surveillance

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  subjects who had abdominal surgery

          -  pregnant or breast feeding
